<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<%-include("../partials/header.ejs")%>
		<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<%-include("../partials/menu.ejs")%>
		<section class="main">
			<div class="left">
				<h1>Welcome!</h1>

				<p><b>Welcome to <i>Blairpath.org</i>!</b> This is a website compiling cartographic data and navigation utilities pertaining to Montgomery Blair High School's campus. Currently, the database contains a total of <span id="roomCounter">?</span> rooms.</p>
				<script>
					$.getJSON("/json/data.json", function (data) {
						document.getElementById("roomCounter").innerHTML = data.rooms.map(f => Object.keys(f).map(s => f[s])).flat(2).length;
					});
				</script>

				<p>More information can be found in the <a href="/about">About</a> page.</p>

				<div class="banner red">
					<p><b>Please note the following:</b> Blairpath is not officially associated with Montgomery Blair High School. Cartographic data on this site have no implicit or explicit claim of accuracy; some information is unverified.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="right">
				<h1>News</h1>
				<div class="banner gray">
