						<b>Apr 17, 2021</b>
						<span style="float: right">Jeffrey Tong</span>
					</p>
					<i>v1.5.0 release notes</i>
					<p>Blairpath now has its own official domain, <a href="blairpath.org">blairpath.org</a>.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="banner gray">
					<p style="text-align: left">
						<b>Mar 28, 2021</b>
