					</p>
					<i>v1.4.0 release notes</i>
					<p>Blairpath's source is now published on GitHub.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="banner gray">
					<p style="text-align: left">
						<b>Mar 28, 2021</b>
						<span style="float: right">Jeffrey Tong</span>
					</p>
					<i>v1.3.0 release notes</i>
					<p>The website has been migrated to Heroku and will soon be hosted on a standalone domain.</p>
